comment: Wood, cacao nibs, citrus, and mild honey on the nose. On the palate, a rush of spice balanced with sweetness, fall spices, slight turpentine, cacao nibs, finishes with dark chocolate that lingers in the finish. Drinks like its proof, maybe even lower. Nicely done. 4/5/2020
Very good.  Will need to taste it again however nice flavor/heat combination.
